{"tid":1054874,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國外交部駐港副特派員會見《明報》總編","createTime":"2019-03-10T07:07:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-10T10:32:48.000Z","uid":70063,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"866145338906b433f8e1f6c67330122b1e369d6c","tid":1054874,"uid":70063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T07:07:28.000Z","msg":"2019年3月7日，宋如安副特派員在公署會見《明報》總編輯梁享南一行。宋介紹了當前涉港外交和公署工作，希望《明報》繼續積極報導國家外交和涉港外交，增進港人對相關問題的了解和認知。雙方還就粵港澳大灣區建設、中美關係等交流看法。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.fmcoprc.gov.hk/chn/gsxw/t1643654.htm?fbclid=IwAR2CzFpelTV5DoPFBj8c1Aazc-3qZ0RKjbumnzLQcxfS3hKnvFo5R1eyZ1Q\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.fmcoprc.gov.hk%2Fchn%2Fgsxw%2Ft1643654.htm%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR2CzFpelTV5DoPFBj8c1Aazc-3qZ0RKjbumnzLQcxfS3hKnvFo5R1eyZ1Q&d=hArt0m4UYatnQvENVNvF2DDyw%2Fr9SRfH8QBX8OZV2FM%3D&h=434210dc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.fmcoprc.gov.hk/chn/gsxw/t1643654.htm?fbclid=IwAR2CzFpelTV5DoPFBj8c1Aazc-3qZ0RKjbumnzLQcxfS3hKnvFo5R1eyZ1Q</a>"},{"pid":"5b3a9e8149deb943bd4b6ba05d5461864d8c4aa1","tid":1054874,"uid":51701,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T07:40:32.000Z","msg":"公信第一, 一早賣左盤變 日月邪報"},{"pid":"fbb96bbb38f8331b3811a59bcc1a45d3e5daae06","tid":1054874,"uid":50457,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T09:26:21.000Z","msg":"難怪紙媒玩完"},{"pid":"39b98c0507aee4607e3a64daac490051a402ca60","tid":1054874,"uid":51937,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T09:38:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2db7b95eb9bb20f8f6963aa9813e5eb2683d114d","tid":1054874,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T10:32:48.000Z","msg":"統戰宣傳你要識做<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又可以畀美國睇一國兩制面目全非<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}